<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Poppa, you amaze me. Other than Selph's final paragraph, he did what should be done--argue that Rush is incorrect by using facts and analysis. Selph's final paragraph was full of fallacy and untruth.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
