My style is... mine.  Thanks for your peace-joy-love counseling, but I will respond in the tone and manner I intend to for both the audience and for the person I am addressing and it will match the context and impact I mean it to.  This is not a mediated timed nor organized debate I will use any tone I choose.
<br />

